&lt;p&gt;Here the correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; Complex.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;intricate&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;means &lt;strong&gt;complex or complicated, &lt;/strong&gt;so the most appropriate synonym to fill in the blank is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;complex.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;An example of an intricate pattern for a dress could be a lacework design or an elaborate embroidery.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Other options and examples:&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Simple &lt;/strong&gt;- The opposite of intricate, a simple pattern could be a plain, solid-colored fabric.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plain &lt;/strong&gt;- A plain pattern is not necessarily intricate or complex, but rather lacking in any design or ornamentation.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ordinary &lt;/strong&gt;- The word &amp;quot;ordinary&amp;quot; means typical or average and does not relate to the complexity of a pattern.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Clear&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The most appropriate synonym of the given word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Facile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Complete&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Transparent&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;If a substance or object is transparent, you can see through it very clearly&amp;nbsp;(यदि कोई पदार्थ या वस्तु पारदर्शी है, तो आप उसके माध्यम से बहुत स्पष्ट रूप से देख सकते हैं)&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;Grow the bulbs in a&lt;strong&gt; transparent&lt;/strong&gt; plastic box, so the children can see the roots growing.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Clear&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;easy to understand, hear, read, or see&amp;nbsp;(समझने, सुनने, पढ़ने या देखने में आसान)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;Can we make the sound any &lt;strong&gt;clearer&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore, as per the points mentioned above, we find that the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Option 1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;Let&amp;#39;s look at the meaning of other words:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Opaque&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;preventing light from travelling through, and therefore not transparent or translucent&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;/span&gt;प्रकाश को यात्रा करने से रोकना, और इसलिए पारदर्शी या पारभासी नहीं&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Pretty&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;quite, but not extremely&amp;nbsp;(काफी, लेकिन बेहद नहीं)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Shiny&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;A shiny surface is bright because it reflects light&amp;nbsp;(एक चमकदार सतह चमकदार होती है क्योंकि यह प्रकाश को परावर्तित करती है)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3) i.e., &amp;#39;Modest&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Conceited&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is an adjective which means&amp;nbsp;excessively proud of oneself; vain.&amp;nbsp;अहंकारी, घमंडी

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​Example -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Fred&amp;#39;s so &lt;strong&gt;conceited&lt;/strong&gt; he&amp;#39;d never believe anyone would refuse him.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The meanings of the given options are as follows:-&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Proud -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;feeling deep pleasure or satisfaction as a result of one&amp;#39;s own achievements, qualities, or possessions or those of someone with whom one is closely associated.&amp;nbsp;किसी उपलब्धि पर हर्षित और संतुष्&amp;zwj;ट; गर्वित या गर्वयुक्त, गौरवान्वित&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Vain -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;having or showing an excessively high opinion of one&amp;#39;s appearance, abilities, or worth.&amp;nbsp;व्&amp;zwj;यर्थ, बेकार; निष्&amp;zwj;फल, बेनतीजा&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Modest -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;unassuming in the estimation of one&amp;#39;s abilities or achievements.&amp;nbsp;विनम्र, विनीत (अपनी क्षमताओं आदि का बखान न करने वाला)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Superior -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;higher in rank, status, or quality.&amp;nbsp;सामान्&amp;zwj;य या अन्&amp;zwj;य से श्रेष्&amp;zwj;ठ, अधिक उत्&amp;zwj;कृष्&amp;zwj;ट&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;From the above meanings, it is evident that&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;modest&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the correct&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;antonym&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;for the word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;conceited.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;Kiosk.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;color: (33, 37, 41); display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;color: (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;kiosk&lt;/strong&gt; is a small, standalone structure or booth typically located in public places, such as malls, airports, or outdoor areas. (सड़क पर बनी बहुत छोटी दुकान जहाँ अख़बार, मिठाइयाँ आदि बिकती है; गुमटी, स्&amp;zwj;टॉल)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It is designed to provide information, services, or products to people in a self-service manner.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The term&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;kiosk&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; can also refer to a small open-fronted hut or pavilion, especially one in a public space for the sale of newspapers, refreshments, or other goods.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;So, a small structure with one or more open sides that is used to vend merchandise is called &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Kiosk.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The correct answer is &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Option 4&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vendor: &lt;/strong&gt;a person who is selling something. (बेचने वाला व्&amp;zwj;यकि्त; विक्रेता)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Podium: &lt;/strong&gt;a small platform for a speaker, a performer, etc. to stand on. (छोटा मंच जिस पर वक्ता, कलाकार आदि खड़े होते हैं)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stand: &lt;/strong&gt;a table or an object that holds or supports something, often so that people can buy it or look at it. (वस्&amp;zwj;तु को टेकने या टिकाने का साधन (कोई मेज़ आदि) (ताकि लोग उस वस्&amp;zwj;तु को देख सकें, ख़रीद सकें); स्&amp;zwj;टैंड)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is-&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Gynaecologist&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;Gynaecologist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is made up of two root words:&lt;strong&gt; Gynae&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and logist.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;gynae&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is related to women.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;​The root word&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;logist&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is used to indicate&amp;nbsp;a person skilled or involved in a branch of study denoted by a noun ending in -logy.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;A gynaecologist&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;a physician or surgeon qualified to practise in gynaecology. (एक स्त्री रोग विशेषज्ञ एक चिकित्सक या सर्जन है जो स्त्री रोग में अभ्यास करने के लिए योग्य है)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;After about six months I decided to see a &lt;strong&gt;gynaecologist&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let us see the meanings of the following&amp;nbsp;root words:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Polyandrist:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;The meaning of the root word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;poly&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; is many. A person&amp;nbsp;who indulges in practices&amp;nbsp;in which a woman has more than one husband. (एक व्यक्ति जो ऐसी प्रथाओं में लिप्त होता है जिसमें एक महिला के एक से अधिक पति होते हैं)

		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Precisely, my diaphanous &lt;strong&gt;polyandrist&lt;/strong&gt;; but it isn&amp;#39;t quite your own affair what you laugh at&amp;mdash;not if I know it!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Monogamy: Monogamy&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;comes from the Greek monogam&amp;iacute;a, from mono-, meaning &amp;ldquo;single&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;one,&amp;rdquo; and -gamy, meaning &amp;ldquo;marriage.&amp;rdquo;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;He believes in &lt;strong&gt;mono&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ga&lt;/strong&gt;my&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
